# ZapLexer 

A lightweight Python package that help student to develop they programming language .

![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.6%2B-blue)
[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/zaplexer.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/zaplexer/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

## Features âœ¨
- Simple API: `from zaplexer import display`
- Built-in file handling from `data/` directory
- Clean terminal output formatting
- Error handling for missing files
- Zero external dependencies

## Installation ðŸ“¦

